Enclosing class:
DualState.PinCount
static final class DualState.PinCount.Manager extends Object implements Supplier<Queue<Thread>>
Open-coded implementation of as much of a Stack as PinCount needs.

A lightweight stack implementation that also pools a few of the objects once pushed on it, for reuse, intended to produce less observed garbage than the earlier straight use of ArrayDeque.
